---
title: Golden Chicken Schnitzel & Wedges with Creamy Slaw
description: Boost the flavour of a classic chicken schnitzel by adding our Aussie spice blend to the golden crumb coating. Served with garlic aioli, potato fries and a creamy slaw for a meal nobody can refuse!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66f4c782587dccd5cb5f1d5c-45ddd4da.jpeg
